    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "When I run flutter on 2 devices like 2 mobile emulators or 1 mobile emulator and Linux, the last one, which is the second one is running doesn't hot reload, when I hit the hot restart button, the new run starts. It's hard to explain this situation, so I made a video for 2 devices, Linux and mobile. This happens as same as mobile and mobile.\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20153831/109770724-28755b00-7c11-11eb-9c5c-4b8662fce246.mp4\r\n\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2021-03-03T11:00:24Z",
